item.title: How can college goalkeepers seamlessly transition to PRO PT2 w/ Maddie Prohaska
item.description: The TKI Crew keeps their Fall Season Rolling Along w/ another smash episode! On Today's Pod TKI's Tori Corsaro and Former USWNT GK Jill Loyden is joined by Maddie Prohaska. The three of them continue the discussion on how college goalkeepers can make a seamless transition from the college to pro game. Great listen for young coaches, players and parents!
